---
title: One-Pot Turkey Soup with Cream and Potatoes
description: Meet our cheeky copycat of an Italian-American restaurant classic! Cozy up to this satisfying soup that's all made in one pot! What more could you want? Garlic bread? You've got it!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soupe-italienne-a-la-dinde-a6e3551b.jpg
